claim: Ruth Negga has appeared in a horror film.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Ruth Negga  (  -LSB- ˈneɪgə -RSB- born 7 January 1982  )  is an Ethiopian born Irish actress , who has appeared in the films Capital Letters  (  2004  )   (  also released as Trafficked in some countries  )  , Isolation  (  2005  )  , Breakfast on Pluto  (  2005  )  and Warcraft  (  2016  )  .
